title: Shenzhou-8 approaching Tiangong-1
description: BEIJING， Nov. 3 (Xinhua) -- Unmanned spacecraft Shenzhou-8 is approaching space lab module Tiangong-1 early Thursday， according to the Beijing Aerospace Flight Control Center.
cleanContent:
The graphics shows the procedure of Shenzhou-8 spacecraft docking with Tiangong-1 space lab module on Nov. 3, 2011. (Xinhua/Lu Zhe)
